title: Visio: Cause and Effect Shapes stencil in Visio for the web [Visio Plan 1, Plan 2]
description: Users with a Visio Plan 1 or Visio Plan 2 license will be able to create cause and effect diagrams, such as fishbone and Ishikawa diagrams, from a blank drawing using the new Cause and Effect Shapes stencil in Visio for the web.
